title: [Dabbings Mews, Mews Lane]
description: The houses edging Mews Lane are charming and well-tended.  Urns containing small hedges sit in front of some, while others boast bright window shutters.  A row of wrought iron street lamps fronts the houses, facing the long wall running parallel to the street on its east side.
paths: Obvious paths: north, south, southwest, west, northwest
